### Get all markets (demo API key)
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/markets
X-RapidAPI-Key: demo-api-key-12345

### Get trending markets
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/markets/trending
X-RapidAPI-Key: demo-api-key-12345

### Get consensus view on Fed rates
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/markets/consensus?topic=Federal%20Reserve
X-RapidAPI-Key: demo-api-key-12345

### Search markets
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/markets/search/semantic?q=recession
X-RapidAPI-Key: demo-api-key-12345

### Analyze a market
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/markets/clx9k2/analyse
X-RapidAPI-Key: demo-api-key-12345
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "analysis_depth": "standard",
  "perspective": "neutral",
  "audience": "general",
  "include_historical_context": true,
  "include_price_drivers": true,
  "include_scenarios": true
}

### Simulate portfolio
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/portfolio/simulate
X-RapidAPI-Key: demo-api-key-12345
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "positions": [
    {
      "market_id": "clx9k2",
      "side": "yes",
      "entry_probability": 0.58,
      "stake": 100,
      "entry_date": "2026-02-01"
    }
  ],
  "cash_balance": 500,
  "include_pnl": true,
  "include_expected_value": true
}

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/health

### Get widget
GET http://localhost:3000/embed/clx9k2